[17/12/2017 18:55:42] <font color="#00ff00">"napravo" y "vlevo",</font>
[17/12/2017 18:55:42] <font color="#00ff00">"izquierda", "derecha"</font>
[17/12/2017 18:55:44] <font color="#00ff00">y "svetofore", que es "semáforo".</font>
